OL,3,CDaniel Craig saves Stroud community
OL,4,Chub from closure with #50k donation
OL,6,FA community hub in Stroud has been
OL,7,Fsaved thanks to a significant donation
OL,8,Ffrom James Bond star Daniel Craig.
OL,10,FThe actor donated #50,000 to help
OL,11,Fsecure the future of social
OL,12,Fenterprises after Brimscombe Mill when
OL,13,Fthe building was put up for sale.
OL,15,FThe mill is home to a number of
OL,16,Fcommunity groups including The Long
OL,17,FTable, The Bike Drop, Kids Stuff and
OL,18,FThe Home Remedy furniture bank.
