OL,3,CDaniel Craig saves Stroud community
OL,4,Chub from closure with #50k donation
OL,6,FThey provide community meals to bring
OL,7,Fpeople together, take unwanted goods
OL,8,Fand give them to those in need and
OL,9,Fcreate a space for people to socialise
OL,10,Fand support each other.
OL,12,FBut the mill's future was thrown into
OL,13,Fdoubt in March when the building was
OL,14,Flisted for sale - putting up to 100
OL,15,Fjobs in jeopardy.
OL,17,FTom Herbert, who founded The Long
OL,18,FTable, said the community hub feared
OL,19,Feviction at the time.
