OL,3,CDaniel Craig saves Stroud community
OL,4,Chub from closure with #50k donation
OL,6,FHe said the community "rallied around"
OL,7,Fthe hub and then "out of the blue"
OL,8,FDaniel Craig offered support.
OL,10,F"In our darkest moment he pledged
OL,11,F#50,000 which has been a war chest, a
OL,12,Flifeline, a godsend," he said. "He
OL,13,Freally has been our real life hero.
OL,14,FWithout that, we wouldn't have been
OL,15,Fable to stay.
OL,17,F"A wonderful local family bought the
OL,18,Fmill so now we can stay here forever."
