OL,3,CDaniel Craig saves Stroud community
OL,4,Chub from closure with #50k donation
OL,6,FHe told ITV News it means The Long
OL,7,FTable - which will serve up 40,000
OL,8,Fcommunity meals by the end of the year
OL,9,F- will continue to thrive.
OL,11,F"The community comes together to make
OL,12,Famazing things happen when we eat
OL,13,Ftogether," he added.
OL,15,FShannon Absalom works at The Long
OL,16,FTable. She said: "I used to come every
OL,17,FFriday morning after baby group which
OL,18,Fis where I met some of my closest
OL,19,Ffriends.
